Shader attributions
===================

crtscreen.glsl
- Corners lifted from fake-crt-geom
- Scanlines/mask/curvature effects lifted from crt-lottes
- Source: https://github.com/libretro/glsl-shaders/tree/master/crt/shaders/fakelottes-geom.glsl
- Local modifications: BUDOSTACK parameter tuning and feature toggles

effects.glsl
- VHS shader by hunterk, adapted from ompuco's AVdistortion shadertoy
- Source: https://github.com/libretro/glsl-shaders/tree/master/vhs/shaders/vhs.glsl
- Local modifications: BUDOSTACK parameter tuning

noise.glsl
- Film noise shader by hunterk
- Source: https://github.com/libretro/glsl-shaders/tree/master/film/shaders/film_noise.glsl
- Local modifications: BUDOSTACK parameter tuning and small algorithm changes.
